## Features
- Users can manage decks of word cards: create, edit, and delete decks
- Users can browse decks in two modes: list and grid


## Front End
- React MUI Typescript Project
- Follow best Front End modern practices
- See package.json for dependencies, suggest installing new dependencies if needed
- Implement features step by step according to instructions to the Agent
- Use Material UI components and styles, follow Documentation https://mui.com/material-ui/getting-started/
- Support responsive layout
- React router is used
- Zustand is state manager
- Formik is form manager

##  Storage
- Dexie is used for IndexedDB storage




